data.description: Are you ready for a Quiet Country Living? This charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is located on 2 acres of land in a quiet, rural setting. The home has hardwood floors throughout, tile in the kitchen, baths, and laundry room, and is in great shape. It is perfect for a growing family or anyone looking for a peaceful place to call home. The main living area features a large living room with a wood burning fireplace, perfect for cozying up on a cold winter night. The backyard is spacious and has plenty of room for outdoor activities, such as a garden, a patio, or a play area for children. Recently built shed in the backyard. Driveway was paved in 2021.
